dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents populated place areas within the United States that include both incorporated places and census designated places identified by the U.S. Census Bureau. Data are represented at 1:100,000 scale. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2.U.S. Populated Place Areas provides areal locations for populated places including fieldsâ€”name, FIPS code, census class, area, and selected demographic data from the U.S. Census.
